George Lloyd (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/George_Lloyd_(actor) 0 George Lloyd (November 5, 1892 – August 15, 1967) was an American character actor. Born in Edinburg, Illinois, Lloyd appeared in over 270 films between 1932 and 1956. George_Lloyd ( November_5_,_1892 – August_15_,_1967 ) was an_American_character_actor .
